Eve On Adams
/$
$
Rooftop Event Venue
/$
$
Private Events and Catering - Tallahassee, FL
/$
/$
/$
$
$
$
$
$
Experience exclusivity and unparalleled views by booking the Full Venue at Eve On Adams. This option offers the entire rooftop restaurant, two bars, indoor dining area, and expansive balcony for large gatherings, accommodating up to 280 guests. The Full Venue provides the ultimate setting for grand celebrations or significant meetings and events.
/$
$
Full Venue
/$
$
/$
/$
/$
$
$
$
The South Terrace boasts a stunning balcony space overlooking the Capitol Building, accommodating up to 80 guests (40 guests seated). This intimate outdoor haven offers a dedicated bar, versatile seating, and picturesque rooftop views. Perfect for private celebrations, cocktail parties, or small corporate events against the city's captivating skyline backdrop.
/$
$
South Terrace
/$
$
/$
/$
/$
$
$
$
The West Terrace offers a cozy, intimate lounge atmosphere with breathtaking skyline views, accommodating up to 25 guests. Ideal for small parties, informal gatherings or relaxed cocktail evenings, this private yet open-air enclave creates memorable moments with exquisite appetizers and signature cocktails, focusing on casual, conversational events.
(Dinner Service not available on West Terrace)
/$
$
West Terrace (Lounge)

$
Our Venue Spaces
/$
$
Located on the 17th floor of the Hilton DoubleTree, Eve On Adams rooftop restaurant offers sophisticated dining and versatile venue spaces.
/$
$
Our exclusive venue spaces are designed to cater to a variety of events, from corporate gatherings to grand celebrations.
/$
/$
/$
$
/$
$
$
$
/$
$
$
Private Events
/$
$
At Eve On Adams, our Private Events team excels in tailoring every detail to your preferences. From elegant sit-down dinners to lively buffet spreads, choose what best fits your event's style, all customizable to match your theme. Our comprehensive services extend to custom menus and sophisticated décor options.
/$
/$
/$
/$
$
$
$
/$
$
$
Off-Site Catering
/$
$
Enjoy our delicious breakfast, lunch, dinner, and dessert cuisine anywhere.
Eve On Adams offers off-site catering with customizable menus for any event size, citywide or beyond. Our dedication to culinary excellence and adaptable service guarantees a memorable experience at your chosen venue.
/$
/$
/$
/$
$
$

$
Set 17 stories above Downtown Tallahassee, Eve On Adams offers an unforgettable dining and lounge atmosphere for you to enjoy while you visit. Located on the 17th floor of the DoubleTree by Hilton, Eve On Adams looks high over the horizon providing a great view of the Tallahassee sunset.
/$
$
Since 2020 our focus has been set on bringing an extraordinary experience to each of our guests. Our staff consists of expert culinary artists, mixologists, and most importantly, a dedicated team who wants to ensure you have a fantastic evening to remember.
